    <title><![CDATA[hexo学习笔记]]></title>
    <link href="http://www.christ2li.com/2015/04/20/hexo%E5%AD%A6%E4%B9%A0%E7%AC%94%E8%AE%B0/"/>
    <id>http://www.christ2li.com/2015/04/20/hexo学习笔记/</id>
    <published>2015-04-20T13:26:51.000Z</published>
    <updated>2015-04-20T14:21:02.821Z</updated>
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>　　本文的目的是记录在用hexo搭建博客时遇到的一些问题和解决方法，因此，内容并非原创，都是针对特定问题<br>而搜索的解决方案。<br><a id="more"></a></p>
<h1 id="打开GitBash输入hexo命令，遇到node:_command_not_found">打开GitBash输入hexo命令，遇到node: command not found</h1><p>　　在安装好hexo和Nodejs第二天，打开打开GitBash输入hexo命令，遇到以下错误：</p>
<pre><code>/C/Administrator/AppData/Roaming/<span class="built_in">npm</span>/<span class="attribute">hexo</span>: <span class="attribute">node</span>: command <span class="keyword">not</span> found
Node <span class="keyword">is</span> <span class="keyword">not</span> <span class="string">'visible'</span> <span class="keyword">in</span> MINGW32 <span class="keyword">by</span> <span class="reserved">default</span>, only <span class="keyword">in</span> the Windows Command Terminal. Same goes <span class="keyword">for</span> <span class="built_in">npm</span>
</code></pre><p>　　出现这种错的原因是Nodejs没有安装正确，环境变量没有设置。<br>　　参考链接分别是<a href="http://stackoverflow.com/questions/8543296/sh-exe-node-command-not-found" target="_blank" rel="external">链接一</a>和<a href="https://users.cs.jmu.edu/bernstdh/web/common/help/cpp_mingw-faq.php" target="_blank" rel="external">链接二</a>。</p>
<h1 id="hexo博客文章头部和侧边栏显示目录">hexo博客文章头部和侧边栏显示目录</h1><h2 id="实现概要">实现概要</h2><h3 id="环境">环境</h3><ul>
<li>hexo3.0；</li>
<li>默认主题light<h3 id="修改或新建的文件">修改或新建的文件</h3></li>
<li><p>themes/light/layout/_partial/article.ejs<br>在&lt;%- item.content %&gt;添加以下代码</p>
  <!-- Table of Contents -->
<pre><code>&lt;% <span class="keyword">if</span> (!index &amp;&amp; <span class="property">item</span>.toc){ %&gt;
  &lt;<span class="keyword">div</span> <span class="property">id</span>=<span class="string">"toc"</span> <span class="type">class</span>=<span class="string">"toc-article"</span>&gt;
     &lt;strong <span class="type">class</span>=<span class="string">"toc-title"</span>&gt;文章目录&lt;/strong&gt;
     &lt;%- toc(<span class="property">item</span>.content) %&gt;
  &lt;/<span class="keyword">div</span>&gt;
&lt;% } %&gt;
&lt;%- <span class="property">item</span>.content %&gt;
</code></pre></li>
<li><p>themes/light/layout/_widget/toc.ejs， 这是侧目录的widget<br>在themes/light/layout/_widget目录下新建一个文件toc.ejs<br>  <div class="widget widget-toc" style="display: none"></div></p>
<pre><code><span class="xml"> <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="title">h3</span> <span class="attribute">class</span>=<span class="value">"title"</span>&gt;</span></span>&lt;%=<span class="ruby"> _<span class="number">_</span>(<span class="string">'Contents'</span>) </span>%&gt;<span class="xml"><span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="title">h3</span>&gt;</span>
   <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="title">div</span> <span class="attribute">class</span>=<span class="value">"container"</span> <span class="attribute">style</span>=<span class="value">"padding: 15px 20px;"</span>&gt;</span>
   <span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="title">div</span>&gt;</span>
<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="title">div</span>&gt;</span></span>&lt;%-<span class="ruby"> js(<span class="string">'js/toc'</span>) </span>%&gt;<span class="xml"></span>
</code></pre></li>
</ul>
<p>在这里需要注意的是要在themes/light/languages/zh-CN.yml 注明：<code>Contents: 目录</code></p>
<ul>
<li><p>themes/light/source/css/_partial/article.styl<br>在themes/light/source/css/_partial/article.styl添加以下代码</p>
<pre><code><span class="comment">/*toc*/</span>
<span class="class">.toc-article</span>
<span class="attribute">background</span> <span class="hexcolor">#eee</span>
<span class="attribute">border</span> <span class="number">1px</span> solid <span class="hexcolor">#bbb</span>
<span class="attribute">border-radius</span> <span class="number">10px</span>
<span class="attribute">margin</span> <span class="number">1.5em</span> <span class="number">0</span> <span class="number">0.3em</span> <span class="number">1.5em</span>
<span class="attribute">padding</span> <span class="number">1.2em</span> <span class="number">1em</span> <span class="number">0</span> <span class="number">1em</span>
<span class="attribute">max-width</span> <span class="number">28%</span>
<span class="class">.toc-title</span>
<span class="attribute">font-size</span> <span class="number">120%</span>
<span class="id">#toc</span>
<span class="attribute">line-height</span> <span class="number">1em</span>
<span class="attribute">font-size</span> <span class="number">0.9em</span>
<span class="attribute">float</span> <span class="attribute">right</span>
<span class="class">.toc</span>
  <span class="attribute">padding</span> <span class="number">0</span>
  <span class="attribute">margin</span> <span class="number">1em</span>
  <span class="attribute">line-height</span> <span class="number">1.8em</span>
  <span class="tag">li</span>
    <span class="attribute">list-style-type</span> <span class="attribute">none</span>
  <span class="class">.toc-child</span> 
  <span class="attribute">margin-left</span> <span class="number">1em</span>
</code></pre></li>
<li><p>themes/light/_config.yml<br>在widgets的配置中增加toc</p>
<blockquote>
<p>widgets:</p>
<ul>
<li>search</li>
<li>category</li>
<li>tag</li>
<li>toc</li>
<li>scrollup</li>
</ul>
</blockquote>
</li>
<li><p>themes/light/source/js/toc.js，代码见<a href="http://qybei.github.io/2015/03/03/hexo%E5%9C%A8%E4%BE%A7%E8%BE%B9%E6%A0%8F%E6%98%BE%E7%A4%BA%E7%9B%AE%E5%BD%95%E7%9A%84%E6%96%B9%E6%B3%95/" target="_blank" rel="external">链接一</a></p>
<h2 id="部署后文章目录显示异常">部署后文章目录显示异常</h2><p>在hexo deploy后，本地的文章头部目录显示正常，而部署后博客文章目录显示不正常，这时需要进入.deploy-git文件夹，执行命令</p>
<p>  git push</p>
</li>
</ul>
<h2 id="参考链接">参考链接</h2><p><a href="http://qybei.github.io/2015/03/03/hexo%E5%9C%A8%E4%BE%A7%E8%BE%B9%E6%A0%8F%E6%98%BE%E7%A4%BA%E7%9B%AE%E5%BD%95%E7%9A%84%E6%96%B9%E6%B3%95/" target="_blank" rel="external">链接一</a></p>
<p><a href="http://kuangqi.me/tricks/enable-table-of-contents-on-hexo/" target="_blank" rel="external">链接二</a></p>
<p><a href="https://github.com/xiangming/landscape-plus" target="_blank" rel="external">链接三</a></p>
]]></content>
